  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK55">
<l>teyvan toḻāaḷ koḻunaṟ ṟoḻuteḻuvāḷ</l>
<l>peyyeṉap peyyu maḻai.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When she who does not worship God, but rises worshiping her husband,</l>
<l>says "rain!"—it rains.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
